00:22:45,550 --> 00:22:46,540
I don't want him to die.

380
00:22:46,540 --> 00:22:47,800
I don't want him to die.

381
00:22:48,970 --> 00:22:49,570
Jin Wujian,

382
00:22:49,570 --> 00:22:51,230
