395
00:23:27,240 --> 00:23:29,110
your lives will be bound together.

396
00:23:29,110 --> 00:23:30,550
You live as one

397
00:23:30,860 --> 00:23:32,410
and die as one.

398
00:23:33,160 --> 00:23:35,640
Just one drop

399
00:23:35,960 --> 00:23:37,720
